&lt;p&gt;Clover Care Services (CCS) is the clinical heart of Clover Health, delivering proactive support and care to our members through our clinical Clover Home Care teams, and quality improvement services to our aligned providers through our Managed Care Organization. We are transforming the healthcare experience by integrating care delivery, provider networks, and clinical programs to improve patient outcomes while managing the total cost of care. CCS functions as a complex, home-based care and managed services organization, leveraging a team-based approach to deliver compassionate, equitable care to members where they are most comfortable: at home.&lt;/p&gt;
