&lt;li&gt;You are located in or willing to travel throughout Monmouth, Mercer, Middlesex, and Somerset Counties, NJ.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You hold (or are willing to obtain) an active New Jersey medical license, DEA registration, and CDS registration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a minimum of 3 years of clinical experience in palliative care, hospice, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
